title: Judge Hears Final Arguments in Suit Over Musk’s Tesla Pay
description: Shareholders’ lawyers challenged the board’s contention that Elon Musk’s record-setting compensation was deserved and an effective tool of motivation.

title: Supreme Court Weighs Tech Company Protections in Google Case
description: The case, concerning a law that gives websites immunity for suits based on their users’ posts, has the potential to alter the very structure of the internet.
